<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Why add an account?</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">Adding your online accounts brings your choice of services like calendar,
  chat, and e-mail straight to your desktop and makes the information of the
  services a seamless part of your user experience. By adding accounts you can
  easily keep in touch using services from different accounts, like chats, at
  the same time. Just set up your online accounts once and every time you start
  your computer all the accounts and services that you have added are ready to
  use.</p>
<p class="p">See <span class="link"><a href="accounts-which-application.html.kn" title="Online services and applications">Online services and applications</a></span> for information on which
  applications can access which online services.</p>
</div>
